FBIS4-27505 "dreas106_c_94017" FBIS-EAS-94-106 Daily Report 23 May 1994 North Korea Radio Denounces ROK Plan To Buy Destroyers Radio Denounces ROK Plan To Buy Destroyers SK2805014494 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network in Korean 1200 GMT 23 May 94 SK2805014494 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network in Korean 1200 GMT 23 May 94 Korean BFN [Text] According to South Korea's CHUNGANG ILBO, the puppet Defense Ministry decided on 13 May to purchase naval destroyers from a foreign country, talking about reinforcement of the Navy. According to the decision, the puppets will introduce three naval destroyers in the country. On 12 May, the South Korean warmongers who are running wild to strengthen Armed Forces for a northward invasion deployed CN-235M, a new-type transport plane recently introduced from a foreign country.
